text: And what’s with all these clothes?

According to my calculations… I need to use a force compatible with this height,

You and that brain of yours.

Watch a real pro chug this stuff.
Get ready, taste buds! Huh? Come out, silly candy!!

Ugh. I guess you won that, Olivia.
Which would you rather choose, pink lollipops or green sour apple candy?
